<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>22</hymn_number>
<author>Upa Rokunga, Doh ia Ab</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Mi banga liengin van mi a hung pieng,
 Lei Bethlehem bawng In a ngak hi;
 Amah chu mihing leh Pathien ahi,
 Lal leh Hukdampa hih a thuoh.

[V2]
 Lawp takin Amah chawian hitiu.
 Ei hukdam dingin a kingainiem;
 A min lopi hen aw lopi pen hen,
 Pathien I kawm a hung tung hi.

[V3]
 2. A lalna thuguk mite'n a het loh.
 Kumsawta Pa angsunga um chu;
 Michingte leh a lalna Aksi tawh.
 Van mipiten a hun phuong tau.

[V4]
 3. Lawpin kiko hitiu Lal thak a pieng,
 Lunggil in Amah chu ho hitiu;
 Edom gimlim leh sana sang inle,
 Lunggil a paucham a lul zawi.</lyrics>
<title>Lal leh Hukdampa</title>
</song>